From: Konstantin Kilzer <konstantin.kilzer@wago.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Sep 2025 13:39:19 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] add GNU-stack section for not executable stack

Add .note.GNU-stack section to fix linker warning:
"missing .note.GNU-stack section implies executable stack"
---
 bl2/aarch32/bl2_el3_entrypoint.S              | 11 +++++++++++
 bl2/aarch32/bl2_el3_exceptions.S              | 11 +++++++++++
 bl32/sp_min/aarch32/entrypoint.S              | 11 +++++++++++
 common/aarch32/debug.S                        | 11 +++++++++++
 drivers/st/uart/aarch32/stm32_console.S       | 11 +++++++++++
